===Proper noun===
'''the Qur’an'''

# The Qur’an (Arabic {{ARchar|أَلْقُرآن}}). Pronounced al-qurʾān.
#(arabic) (literal meaning) the recitation.
#The [[Islamic]] holy book, considered to be God’s message for mankind, revealed to [[Muhammad]].
#A copy of this book.

